[FeaturePcd]
  gEfiMdeModulePkgTokenSpaceGuid.PcdFrameworkCompatibilitySupport         ## CONSUMES

[Depex]
  gEfiPeiMemoryDiscoveredPpiGuid AND gEfiPeiBootInRecoveryModePpiGuid

